<http://example.org/paracetamol-recipe/process/operation/React> a cmcpo:CMC_1000140 .

<http://example.org/paracetamol-recipe/process/stage/Synthesis> a <http://purl.allotrope.org/ontologies/process#AFP_0001348> .

<http://example.org/paracetamol-recipe/process/operation/Fill> a cmcpo:CMC_1000167 .

